Zend_Db_Mapper Proposal Prototype
=================================

See proposal: http://framework.zend.com/wiki/display/ZFPROP/Zend_Db_Mapper+-+Benjamin+Eberlei

1. Running Unittests:

In tests/Zend/Entity/ScenarioData/Clinic grab the database.sql and put
it into your MySQL Database. Open up the Zend_Entity_Adapter_PDO_MySQL_ClinicScenario
and change the options for the Database connection.

Do:
cd tests/
phpunit Zend_Entity_AllTests

2. See embedded Zend_Test_PHPUnit_Database proposal

Embedded into this proposal is a conversion of the PHPUnit Database Extension
to work with Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract and add some convenience functionality that
is offered by Zend_Db over PDO.

http://framework.zend.com/wiki/display/ZFPROP/Zend_Test_PHPUnit_Database+-+Benjamin+Eberlei